
Setup OpenJMS as external JMS provider for OFBiz:

1) Download openjms-0.7.2
2) Extract openjms in work directory
3) Copy ofbiz/setup/openjms/config/ofb_jms.xml to $OPENJMS_HOME/config
4) Run $OPENJMS_HOME/bin/startjms.sh -config $OPENJMS_HOME/config/ofb_jms.xml

Be sure to configure serviceengine.xml to use the OpenJMS JNDI provider.

